               stealing, 9 yards of printed furniture, value 12s.; 3 yards of cotton, value 18d.; 1 pillow-case, value 1s.; 1 pillow-ticking, value 1s.; 1 pair of stockings, value 2s.; 1 night-cap, value 6d.; 4 towels, value 3s.; 1 chair-cover, value 18d.; 1 table-cover. value 3s.; 1 sofa-cover, value 1s.; 2 books, value 2s.; 28lbs. of feathers, value 2l. 16s.; 1 handkerchief, value 18d.; 1 blanket, value 5s.; 1 sheet, value 4s.; 3 saucers, value 18d.; 3 plates, value 18d.; 1 teapot stand, value 6d.; 1 dish, value 18d.; 1 mug, value 6d.; 1 glass-lamp, value 2d.; 1 wine-glass, value 2d.; 1 root-glass, value 4d.; 7 pieces of bed-furniture, value 20s.; 1 carpet-cover, value 5s.; 3 glass-cruets, value 1s.; 1 foot-bath, value 2s.; 1 jelly mould, value 5s.; 1 toasting-fork, value 6d.; 1 steel, value 6d.; 1 cloak-pin, value 1d.; 2 bell-pulls, value 6d.; 1 lamp-hook, value 2d., and 1 weight, value 6d., the goods of 
                     
