                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. On the 13th of October I went with the prosecutor to the prisoner's house, with a search-warrant; what has been stated is correct.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. My prosecutor said he wished me to clear the rubbish out of the house, before my mistress came home, which induced me to take more than I should have done.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 28.</p>
